title: Ambisonic Parks and Residential Ambisonic FOA /Stereo
description: 28 HD Sound Effects with a large selection of Parks, Forests and Residential
longDescription:
From 24/96 Sound Effects. Immersive Parks and Residential continues a series started with Immersive Parks and Forests, features 26 more HD 24bit/96khz Surround Sound Effects with a large selection of Parks, Residential Areas and City Rain.

Most of the tracks were captured in Los Angeles during the 2020 Corona Virus shutdown, so the ambiances are quieter with less human activity.

Recorded with a Voyage Audio 2nd Order Spatial Microphone.Mastered with ProTools Ultimate in 2 configurations: Ambisonic (Ambix 1st Order (Wyzx) and Stereo (L-R)Most tracks are 2-3 Minutes in length with embedded metadata. All new, original recordings. Here the Demo track here on SoundCloud

Need O2A 9 channel 2nd Order Ambisonic? We offer free upgrades for the tracks, contact us at 2496sfx.com
